<P>
   Byears, playing a reserve role after starting in her first three
seasons in the league, helped Sacramento's backups outscore
Seattle's subs 37-8. Reserves Katy Steding and Stacy Clinesmith
each had 10 points for the Monarchs.
</P>
<P>
   Monarchs All-Star guard Ruthie Bolton-Holifield was in uniform,
but did not play because of a strained right knee.
</P>
<P>
