<HEADLINE> Dow Gains 20; Nasdaq Climbs 71  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK (AP) -- The Dow Jones industrial average is up 20 points
in today's early going. Advancing issues on the New York Stock
Exchange hold a 3-2 lead over decliners.
</P>
<P>
   The Nasdaq Composite Index is ahead 71 points and the Standard &AMP;
Poor's 500 Stock Index is up six points.
</P>
